data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! New Roof(2021) & Brand New AC.  This stunning 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom property is the perfect retreat for first-time homebuyers or investors seeking a private oasis. Tucked away in a serene corner and secured within a gated community. This delightful home has been thoughtfully updated, boasting fully redone bathrooms & new flooring,  The open and inviting floor plan provides ample space to entertain and unwind in comfort.  Homeowners can also enjoy resort-style amenities at the well-appointed clubhouse, complete with a sparkling pool and lush, tropical landscaping. This exclusive community has no age restrictions, making it a fantastic place for people of all life stages to call home.
